Overland_Park.Vox Theatre:
The Vox Theatre is an event space located in Rosedale, Kansas.


== The Vox Theatre ==


=== History ===
The Vox Theatre opened as the Rosedale Theatre on December 20, 1922 as a silent movie theater. The Rosedale Theatre was originally owned by T.L. Ricksecker and cost $30,000 to construct.
